│ The log shows that SCCP is merging a constant `<2 x i1> splat (i1 true)` into the fcmp instruction, which indicates that the constant folding logic in ValueLatticeElement::getCompare() is returning a        │
│ constant when it shouldn't for dynamic denormal modes.                                                                                                                                                         │
│                                                                                                                                                                                                                │
